creator: Erin M.
descriptionHtml:
With the Jones Soda app, you have exclusive access to your favourite craft soda company.

REEL LABELS: Ever wonder what the story is behind the photo on a Jones label? Introducing REEL LABELS! After 25 years, we decided to take our labels to the next level. Download the Jones Soda App to see each Reel Label come to life through augmented reality video. Think you've got a story worth sharing? Submit your own short video and it could be a Reel blockbuster!

SUBMIT CONTENT: Upload your photo or video to our Jones Soda Gallery and if we like it we might use it for one of our labels!

VIEW GALLERY: See photo and video submissions.

FIND JONES: Jonesing for some soda? Use the store locator!

BUY JONES: Jonesing for some soda and couldn't find it? Shop online!
